This is a simple To-do application done for Web3Bridge pre- qualification Excercise
the input box takes takes the task to be achieved, any achievedtask can be checked
there is a delete icon to remove any task that needed to e removed
the input box takes the new rask and append it in the list of to-do
there is uiid to notify user if their is an existing task as the in one when user click on add button
their is a pge for each task descripton
user can edit previous task
there is a model to notify user for any action they take I.E CRUD
